('d93eccc2-26c9-45cc-bb79-4f45f0ad96ba', 'Prevagen: The Pharmacy Counter Favorite', 'Prevagen is one of the most recognizable memory supplements in America. While its apoaequorin ingredient is unique, the evidence base remains limited compared to competitors.', 'Apoaequorin is a calcium-binding protein originally from jellyfish. Vitamin D3 at 50mcg supports overall brain health. Intentionally simple formula.', ARRAY['Widely available nationwide', 'Simple one-pill daily formula', 'No stimulants or interactions', 'Gentle and well-tolerated'], 'Take 1 capsule daily, preferably in the morning.', ARRAY['Limited clinical evidence for apoaequorin', 'FTC has questioned some marketing claims', 'Premium pricing for a simple formula'], 'May benefit older adults with mild age-related memory concerns, though expectations should be tempered.', 'Mind Lab Pro for evidence-based nootropic. NooCube for better value.', 'Q: Does it actually work? A: Clinical evidence is limited. Some users report benefits but the FTC has questioned certain claims. Q: Is it safe? A: Good safety profile with minimal reported side effects.', 6.8, '[{"name": "Dorothy M.", "rating": 4, "text": "I have taken it for 6 months and my husband says I seem sharper. No side effects at all.", "verified": true, "date": "2026-01-05"}, {"name": "Frank P.", "rating": 3, "text": "Have not noticed much change. My doctor said it is safe but suggested other options too.", "verified": true, "date": "2025-12-15"}]'::jsonb),

