('9f042aa9-762d-4f65-883c-b50af8885184', 'Ghost Whey: Best Flavors in the Game', 'Ghost has revolutionized supplements with licensed candy flavor collaborations. Beyond the hype, Ghost Whey delivers solid 25g protein with digestive enzymes and a transparent label.', 'A blend of whey isolate, concentrate, and hydrolysate provides 25g per scoop. Added digestive enzymes improve tolerance.', ARRAY['Incredible licensed flavors (Oreo, Chips Ahoy)', 'Fully transparent label', 'Added digestive enzymes', '25g protein per scoop'], 'Mix 1 scoop with 6-8 oz cold water or milk.', ARRAY['Licensed flavors use artificial ingredients', 'Blend is not pure isolate', 'Premium brand pricing'], 'Built for fitness enthusiasts who care about flavor experience as much as macros.', 'ON Gold Standard for better value. Transparent Labs for clean ingredients.', 'Q: What is the best flavor? A: Oreo and Chips Ahoy are fan favorites. Peanut Butter Cereal Milk is the dark horse. Q: Is it just marketing? A: No, 25g protein per scoop with transparent labeling is legitimate.', 8.6, '[{"name": "Jake C.", "rating": 5, "text": "The Oreo flavor is INSANE. I genuinely look forward to my post-workout shake now.", "verified": true, "date": "2026-01-09"}, {"name": "Brittany N.", "rating": 4, "text": "Best tasting protein ever but I wish it was a pure isolate.", "verified": true, "date": "2025-12-19"}]'::jsonb),

