('d4ba1363-c13e-433b-8108-9b8c4ed3bdc5', 'Vega Sport Premium: Performance Plant Protein', 'Vega Sport Premium delivers 30g multi-source plant protein with added BCAAs, probiotics, and tart cherry. A solid all-in-one for plant-based athletes.', 'Four plant protein sources provide 30g complete protein. 2 billion CFU probiotics support gut health. Tart cherry and turmeric for recovery.', ARRAY['30g plant protein per serving', 'Added probiotics (2 billion CFU)', 'Tart cherry for recovery', 'NSF Certified for Sport'], 'Mix 1 scoop with 10-12 oz cold water or plant milk. Best blended.', ARRAY['Chalky texture compared to whey', 'Stevia taste not for everyone', 'Premium pricing'], 'Solid choice for plant-based athletes who want probiotics and recovery ingredients in their protein.', 'Garden of Life Sport for organic option. Orgain for budget plant protein.', 'Q: How does it compare to Garden of Life Sport? A: Similar protein. Vega adds probiotics while Garden of Life adds more recovery botanicals. Q: Is the stevia taste strong? A: Chocolate masks it better than vanilla.', 8.2, '[{"name": "Diana W.", "rating": 4, "text": "Love having probiotics in my protein. The Mocha flavor is the best plant protein flavor I have tried.", "verified": true, "date": "2026-01-04"}, {"name": "Raj P.", "rating": 4, "text": "Good protein for plant-based athletes. Texture is improving with each new formulation.", "verified": true, "date": "2025-12-16"}]'::jsonb);